## Tailwind Config

Add these to your `tailwind.config.js`:

```js
module.exports = {
  theme: {
    extend: {
      colors: {
        brand: {
          primary: '{{primary_color}}',
          secondary: '{{secondary_color}}',
          accent: '{{accent_color}}'
        }
      },
      fontFamily: {
        heading: ['{{font_heading}}', {{heading_fallback_array}}],
        body: ['{{font_body}}', {{body_fallback_array}}]
      }
    }
  }
}
```
